Privacy Policy for PwnDroid

Last updated: July 05, 2025

This Privacy Policy describes Our policies and procedures on the collection, use and disclosure of Your information when You use the Application and tells You about Your privacy rights and how the law protects You.

**IMPORTANT NOTICE: PwnDroid is a local security research and educational tool. This application is designed to operate primarily on your local device with minimal data collection. This policy reflects our commitment to privacy-by-design principles.**

We use Your Personal data only as necessary to provide the Application's functionality. By using the Application, You agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this Privacy Policy.
